# %UNUSED Section
# This section enumerates the unused ranges of each CLASS. Each entry
# is described on a single line as follows:
#    <class name> <range> <delta>
# Addresses given in the range are in hexadecimal and units of delta.
%UNUSED
RAM 6C-6F 1
RAM 110-16F 1
RAM 1B0-1EF 1
BANK0 6C-6F 1
BANK2 110-16F 1
BANK3 1B0-1EF 1
CONST 3-3 2
CONST 800-800 2
CONST 1016-13E7 2
CONST 1800-1FFF 2
ENTRY 3-3 2
ENTRY 800-800 2
ENTRY 1016-13E7 2
ENTRY 1800-1FFF 2
IDLOC 2000-2003 2
CODE 3-3 2
CODE 800-800 2
CODE 1016-13E7 2
CODE 1800-1FFF 2
SFR0 0-1F 1
SFR1 80-9F 1
